    GUIParameterFile
    This class takes a File or InputStreamReader object as a reference and opens and read the existing parameter file: It reads all lines and creates a ParmEntry object for every to store the information. It stores the read values by the name of the entry.

    GUIParameterFile
    This class takes a File or InputStreamReader object as a reference and opens and read the existing parameter file: It reads all lines and creates a ParmEntry object for every to store the information. It stores the read values by the name of the entry.
    SiccomUI
    The GUI for Siccom.java
    TimedDisplayAlgorithm
    This class implements an algorithm that will compute a periodically visual update during simulation time instead after every or an amount of steps.
    The Schedule class simplifies the process to implement this simple extension because the method TimedDisplayAlgorithm.visualUpdate(SimState) is only called once for a time on the time scale: several event with the same time are processed in a single step.
